<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Admin Dashboard</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/ui.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans text-gray-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-8 bg-white shadow-sm rounded-xl">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-brand mb-6 border-b border-brand pb-2">
          Welcome,
          <% if (user && user.business && user.business.name) { %>
            <%= user.business.name %>
          <% } else if (user && user.email) { %>
            <%= user.email %>
          <% } else { %>
            Admin
          <% } %>
          !
        </h1>

        <p class="text-gray-600">Manage your AI agent settings and view captured leads from this dashboard.</p>

        <div class="grid gap-6 mt-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="dashboard-card card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transform transition duration-200 hover:scale-105">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">⚙️ Agent Settings</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Configure your AI agent's personality, welcome message, and appearance.</p>
                <a href="/admin/settings" class="text-brand font-medium hover:underline">Manage Agent Settings</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dashboard-card card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transform transition duration-200 hover:scale-105">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">❓ Client Intake Questions</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Set up the questions your AI agent will ask to capture lead information.</p>
                <a href="/admin/lead-questions" class="text-brand font-medium hover:underline">Manage Intake Questions</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dashboard-card card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transform transition duration-200 hover:scale-105">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">📚 Knowledge Base</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Add and manage the information your AI agent uses to answer customer questions.</p>
                <a href="/admin/knowledge-base" class="text-brand font-medium hover:underline">Manage Knowledge Base</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dashboard-card card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transform transition duration-200 hover:scale-105">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">👥 Clients & Requests</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">View and manage all leads captured by your AI agent.</p>
                <a href="/admin/leads" class="text-brand font-medium hover:underline">View Clients / Requests</a>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-card card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transform transition duration-200 hover:scale-105">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">🔔 Notification Settings</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Configure where you receive notifications when new leads are captured.</p>
                <a href="/admin/notifications" class="text-brand font-medium hover:underline">Manage Notifications</a>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-card card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transform transition duration-200 hover:scale-105">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">🗂️ Projects</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">View and manage all projects synced from your PM tool.</p>
                <a href="/admin/projects" class="text-brand font-medium hover:underline">Manage Projects</a>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-card card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transform transition duration-200 hover:scale-105">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">🔗 Integrations</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Connect your project management and messaging tools.</p>
                <a href="/admin/integrations" class="text-brand font-medium hover:underline">View Integrations</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-10 pt-6 border-t">
            <a href="/api/admin/logout" class="inline-block text-red-600 border border-red-600 rounded px-4 py-2 hover:bg-red-600 hover:text-white transition">Logout</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 